</div><br />
Categories not mentioned so far include:<br />
<br />
* Divine Arbitration (not technically a heal but certainly relevant to healing)<br />
* Long Range Heals (critically important for certain encounters)<br />
* "Contingency Heal" buffs (e.g. Divine Intervention)<br />
* Damage Absorbers (e.g. Enchanter runes, Bulwark of Vie)<br />
* Regen<br />
<br />
Where are you going with this?</div>
		<!-- / message -->
	
		
		
		
