		<!-- message -->
		<div>Do you think that removing CH from the current game will fix Chain healing ? I doubt it. Once we remove CH people will use the next big heals in chains. The current encounters often focus on massisve DPS focused on 1 or 2 chars. As long as that kind of encounters exists Chains will be there. Either with CH or more tight chains with patches.<br />
<br />
A chain is the most effective way of healing that kind of encounter because it most evenly spreads the mana loss and agro over all in th chain.<br />
<br />
If you want to get rid of CH's you need to change all encounters where most dps is done to just a few chars. There should perhaps be more LDON raid type of encounters. CH's were not as muched needed there</div>
		<!-- / message -->
	
		
		
		
